title: Financial Safari interview
author: VD
content_html: Coach Pete of the Financial Safari interviewed me about SJWs Always Lie. He’s a smart guy and it was a pretty good interview, although it was very late by my time and my verbal tic discipline was nonexistent. Which is to say that my comments are punctuated by a lot of “you knows”.
